---
title: Homestyle Pork & Veggie Fries with Caramelised Onion Sauce & Radish Salad
description: Seasoned, seared and sliced, this pork is too good to pass up on a chance to show it off. Serve with veggie fries and a
caramelised onion sauce over the top to get those mouths watering. Bring it home with a peppy radish salad!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
